601
00:40:31,375 --> 00:40:33,083
mungkin akan tetap bertemu.

602
00:40:33,167 --> 00:40:34,708
Tikus?

603
00:40:35,708 --> 00:40:36,625
Ide bagus!

604
00:40:37,375 --> 00:40:38,875
Tikus!

605
00:40:40,333 --> 00:40:41,625
Kau juga tahu.

