660
00:44:37,583 --> 00:44:39,000
Kau yakin soal ini?

661
00:45:08,708 --> 00:45:11,042
<i>Jaga pikiranmu tetap fokus.</i>

662
00:45:11,125 --> 00:45:13,167
<i>Jangan dikendalikan kekuatanmu.</i>

663
00:45:24,625 --> 00:45:25,625
Maaf.

664
00:45:46,208 --> 00:45:47,125
Mau apa?

665
00:45:47,208 --> 00:45:48,375
Lanjutkan saja.

666
00:46:24,083 --> 00:46:25,125
Ayo.

